text: Selena O'Hanlon (born March 21, 1981) is a Canadian equestrian who competes in the sport of eventing.COC ProfileFei profile ==Olympics== O'Hanlon competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics in Beijing, finishing 45th in the individual event and 9th in the team event. In July 2016, she was named to Canada's Olympic team. However on July 29 she was withdrawn from her team due to an injury to her horse Foxwood High. ==References== ==External links== *Official website Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Canadian female equestrians Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Equestrians at the 2011 Pan American Games
